import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"create-and-use-mock-twitter"}}>{`Create and use mock twitter`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Navigate `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://app.graphqleditor.com/showcase/fake-twitter"}}>{`https://app.graphqleditor.com/showcase/fake-twitter`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Click Code in top left corner`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Switch from `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`graphql`}</MDXTag>{` to `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`typescript`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Click Copy Icon on Code pan`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Paste the code to `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`some-ts-file-inside-your-project.ts`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Click Faker Cloud on website`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`You should be navigated to `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://faker.graphqleditor.com/showcase/fake-twitter/graphql"}}>{`https://faker.graphqleditor.com/showcase/fake-twitter/graphql`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`This is the interface of fake backend here you can test your graphql queries with GraphiQL. You can use this graphql endpoint to get fake responses. If you want to get type safe responses:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-tsx"}}>{`import { api } from './some-ts-file-inside-your-project';
const Api = api('https://faker.graphqleditor.com/showcase/fake-twitter/graphql');
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Now you should get autocomplete responses from `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`Api`}</MDXTag>{` object`}</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
